metadata.name: Newborn
metadata.description:
In my culture , making a family and giving birth is some thing really holly and we all have to make families and babies as our fathers taught us .Our fathers and previous generations never had a fear about financial issues and never had issues with training and rising a baby and in their Idea a newborn baby brings blessing and its own wealth to this world .... This piece was drawn with color pencils and took about more than 4 months , but the calm ness of drawing with colorpencils released the good feelings in my soul .
size: 100x70 cm
technique: colorpencil
